---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kaleb Resume | Dunn-Keaney">
    <article class="max-w-5xl">
        <section class="paper-panel mb-6">
            <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Resume</p>
            <h1 class="mb-4">Kaleb Dunn</h1>
            <p class="max-w-3xl mb-5">
                Strategy and Operations professional translating analysis into operating decisions across healthcare, financial services, and
                industrial environments.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-1 text-sm text-primary/75">
                <p><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/kaleb-dunn" class="no-underline">linkedin.com/in/kaleb-dunn</a></p>
                <p><a href="mailto:kalebdunn@gmail.com" class="no-underline">kalebdunn@gmail.com</a></p>
                <p>Nashville, TN (Open to Relocation)</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="paper-panel mb-3">
            <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Core Positioning</p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl mb-3">Strategy, Operations, and Delivery Leadership</h2>
            <p class="max-w-3xl">
                Analytics, execution leadership, and operating-model thinking for better prioritization, visibility, and delivery in ambiguous
                settings.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
            <div class="paper-panel">
                <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Delivery Context</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-serif">Cross-Functional Programs</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-primary/70">Business, product, and technical teams aligned around execution.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="paper-panel">
                <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Industries</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-serif">Healthcare, Financial Services, Industrial</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-primary/70">Cross-domain operational and delivery leadership.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="paper-panel">
                <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Decision Systems</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-serif">KPI and Governance Support</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-primary/70">Risk framing, prioritization, and reporting for leadership decisions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="paper-panel">
                <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Execution Strength</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-serif">Complex Program Delivery</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-primary/70">Turning ambiguity into reliable operating rhythm and outcomes.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="paper-panel mb-6">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl">Summary</h2>
            <p>
                Strategy and Operations professional with experience translating analysis into operating decisions across healthcare, financial
                services, and industrial environments. Combines analytics, execution leadership, and operating-model thinking to improve
                prioritization, visibility, and delivery in ambiguous settings.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="paper-panel mb-6">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl">Experience</h2>
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="border-l pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
                    <p class="eyebrow text-primary mb-2">Aug 2024-Present</p>
                    <h3 class="mb-1">Senior Associate, Strategy and Performance</h3>
                    <p class="mb-3 text-base text-primary/85">Ankura</p>
                    <p class="mb-3">
                        Partner with client and delivery leaders to prioritize investments, resolve delivery risk, and translate analysis into
                        operating decisions across multiple industries.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
                        <li>
                            Shaped investment and governance decisions for a $30M clinical technology portfolio by synthesizing a 200-system
                            landscape across 300+ sites in 20 states into roadmap options and governance-ready recommendations.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Flagged pay-data inaccuracies across 34,000 clinicians and prioritized approximately 500 highest-risk cases for
                            remediation.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Isolated two drivers causing 80% of denials and built estimate-to-claim-to-denial matching in SQL and Excel to support
                            fixes and disputes.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Directed backlog prioritization and sprint planning for a 20-person rewards product team, improving throughput by 20%
                            through refined work intake, velocity planning, and decision discipline.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Stabilized execution for a roughly 10-person Salesforce claims team by instituting operating cadence, delivery
                            visibility, and team norms during module buildout.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="border-l pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
                    <p class="eyebrow text-primary mb-2">Feb 2022-Oct 2023</p>
                    <h3 class="mb-1">Consultant</h3>
                    <p class="mb-3 text-base text-primary/85">Razorleaf Corporation</p>
                    <p class="mb-3">
                        Led PLM/SPDM configuration and integration workstreams for industrial clients, translating business requirements into
                        deployed workflows and system behavior to support implementation outcomes.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
                        <li>
                            Managed 4+ concurrent projects and clients, maintaining stakeholder communication while leading custom architectural
                            design and implementation work.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Built internal tools and extensions that reduced manual effort, improved delivery efficiency, and increased team capacity
                            through reusable implementation assets and peer training.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="paper-panel mb-6">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl">Education</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="border-l pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
                    <strong>Purdue University</strong> - Master of Engineering Management (2024)
                </li>
                <li class="border-l pl-4" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
                    <strong>Purdue University</strong> - B.S. Industrial Engineering (2022)
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="paper-panel">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl">Skills</h2>
            <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                <p class="text-sm">
                    <strong>Strategy and Ops:</strong> Operating cadence, KPI and process design, roadmap and prioritization, stakeholder alignment.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                    <strong>Execution:</strong> Product Owner, sprint planning, backlog refinement, workshop facilitation.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                    <strong>Analytics:</strong> SQL, root cause and Pareto analysis, Excel modeling, dashboarding.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                    <strong>Tools:</strong> Excel, PowerPoint, Azure DevOps, Smartsheet, Figma, Python, C#, JavaScript, Postman.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </article>
</Layout>
